===制作===
《荣耀战魂》是由[[育碧蒙特利尔|育碧蒙特利尔]]开发的，[[Ubisoft_Blue_Byte|Blue Byte]]工作室负责了其中的PC版本开发。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://blog.ubi.com/honoring-pc-legacy/|title=Honoring a PC Legacy - UbiBlog - Ubisoft®|date=2016-08-15|newspaper=UbiBlog - Ubisoft®|accessdate=2017-09-22|language=en-us|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322093745/https://blog.ubi.com/honoring-pc-legacy/|archivedate=2017-03-22}}</ref>该游戏的开发工作始于2012年，《荣耀战魂》是这家公司首次尝试开发策略-动作类游戏。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/06/15/e3-2015-ubisoft-announces-new-ip-for-honor/153967/|title=E3 2015:  Ubisoft Announces New IP ‘For Honor’-Hardcore Gamer|accessdate=2017-09-22|author=|date=|work=www.hardcoregamer.com|publisher=|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224195318/https://hardcoregamer.com/2015/06/15/e3-2015-ubisoft-announces-new-ip-for-honor/153967/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该游戏的架构受到了[[射击游戏|射击游戏]]启发。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://blog.ubi.com/for-honor-deep-dive/|title=What is For Honor? - UbiBlog - Ubisoft®|date=2015-06-15|newspaper=UbiBlog - Ubisoft®|accessdate=2017-09-22|language=en-us|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616052336/http://blog.ubi.com/for-honor-deep-dive/|archivedate=2015-06-16}}</ref>育碧在[[E3_2015|E3 2015]]上公布了这一作品并放出了预告片（{{lang|en|CGI trailer}}）和游戏的演示版（{{lang|en|gameplay demo}}）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/06/15/ubisoft-announces-new-viking-samurai-game-called-for-honor.aspx|title=Ubisoft Announces New Viking/Samurai Game Called For Honor|accessdate=2017-09-22|work=Game Informer|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225124902/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/06/15/ubisoft-announces-new-viking-samurai-game-called-for-honor.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/06/15/for-honor-e3-2015-ubisoft-trailer-gameplay-video/|title=For Honor announced at Ubisoft E3 2015 – trailer, gameplay|newspaper=VG247.com|accessdate=2017-09-22|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302232756/https://www.vg247.com/2015/06/15/for-honor-e3-2015-ubisoft-trailer-gameplay-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年2月14日，该游戏在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]，[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台同步上面向全球发布。<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=http://za.ign.com/for-honor/91678/preview/e3-2015-hands-on-impressions-of-ubisofts-for-honor|title=E3 2015: Hands-on impressions of Ubisoft's For Honor|date=2015-06-16|newspaper=IGN Africa|accessdate=2017-09-22|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225144344/https://za.ign.com/for-honor/91678/preview/e3-2015-hands-on-impressions-of-ubisofts-for-honor|dead-url=no}}</ref>游戏的配乐原声由电影作曲家丹尼·本西（Danny Bensi）和桑德·朱利安斯（Saunder Jurriaans）创作。包含20首曲子的游戏配乐原声带于当日一同发布。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.vgmonline.net/exclusive-know-the-composers-preview-the-soundtrack-for-for-honor/|title=Know the composers, preview the soundtrack for For Honor|date=2017-02-02|newspaper=VGMO -Video Game Music Online-|accessdate=2017-09-22|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811011810/http://www.vgmonline.net/exclusive-know-the-composers-preview-the-soundtrack-for-for-honor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

